flowchart TB
AG["agent action<br/>file write · command"] ==> PT["PRETOOL<br/>short-lived hook, before execution"]
PT ==> M["compute_severity<br/>the same engine in both layers<br/>Clean · Suspicious · Malicious"]
DA["DAEMON<br/>background service, watches the filesystem"] ==> M
M ==>|"hostile at write-time"| B["exit 2<br/>blocks the write before it touches the disk"]
M ==>|"malicious on disk"| QA["quarentena<br/>moves, does not delete: reversible"]
QA ==> HU["human decides<br/>list · show · restore · purge"]
M -.-> N["Two layers, one engine: the pretool acts before (sync),<br/>the daemon acts after (async). Nothing is deleted without a human decision."]

